Evaluation-Only Notice

The materials in this repository are provided for research review, educational discussion, theoretical evaluation, and reproducibility-oriented experimentation.

They are not provided as experimental active-matter validation, biological/social-system validation, swarm-control technology, crowd-control technology, safety-certified control software, or civilization-scale modeling.

Any applied, experimental, biological, social, robotic, industrial, safety-critical, or public-policy use requires independent expert review and domain-specific validation.

